1. *Igra* se odvija u dvorištu njegove kuće. (The game is taking place in his yard.)
2. Njegov brat je u potpunosti zaglibio u *igri*. (His brother is completely absorbed in the game.)
3. Deca su se udružila da bi zajedno igrala *igru*. (The children joined together to play the game together.)
4. On je uvek bio najbolji u *igri*. (He was always the best at the game.)
5. Ona je pobedila svoju sestru u zabavnoj *igri*. (She beat her sister in a fun game.)
6. Ona je stvorila tačne pravila za tu *igru*. (She created exact rules for that game.)
7. *Igra* je bila veoma napeta. (The game was very tense.)
8. Oni su se igrali *igru* u parku. (They were playing the game in the park.)
9. On je voleo da se *igra* u pauzama između časova. (He liked to play during the breaks between classes.)
10. Ona je bila izvor zabave za sve jer je uvek voljela da *igra*. (She was a source of fun for everyone because she always loved to play.)